00:22:38.820 --> 00:22:41.880
out very prominently, and then
the background information of

00:22:41.880 --> 00:22:45.250
the map is really sinking back
for context, and it's not

00:22:45.250 --> 00:22:46.680
grabbing your attention.

00:22:46.680 --> 00:22:50.280
So how can we create something
like this?

00:22:50.280 --> 00:22:51.840
We'll start back with
the base map.

00:22:51.840 --> 00:22:54.470
Now I suppose the obvious thing
to do is probably just

00:22:54.470 --> 00:22:56.850
to desaturate this map
completely and

00:22:56.850 --> 00:22:57.940
get rid of the labels.

00:22:57.940 --> 00:23:01.150
So let's give that a try.

00:23:01.150 --> 00:23:03.060
SCOTT SHAWCROFT: So here you can
