00:23:07.280 --> 00:23:08.490
We have two styles here.

00:23:08.490 --> 00:23:10.840
First, we have one that
has no element type

00:23:10.840 --> 00:23:12.140
and no feature type.

00:23:12.140 --> 00:23:15.090
This means that it applies to
everything on the map, and so

00:23:15.090 --> 00:23:17.870
we're desaturating
that by 100%.

00:23:17.870 --> 00:23:22.590
We have a second style that is
restricted to only labels.

00:23:22.590 --> 00:23:26.900
And for that, we turn them
all off using visibility.

