And we'll go back to the
first principle.

00:23:54.920 --> 00:23:57.420
And first of all, we'll remove
some of the unnecessary

00:23:57.420 --> 00:23:58.390
information.

00:23:58.390 --> 00:24:01.850
So the most obvious candidate
