00:35:54.250 --> 00:35:57.510
And then after half a second,
when the full JavaScript map

00:35:57.510 --> 00:35:59.130
loads, I'd replace it,
and hopefully the

00:35:59.130 --> 00:36:00.040
user wouldn't notice.

