00:36:03.230 --> 00:36:06.460
SCOTT SHAWCROFT: So for those
of you watching at home, the

00:36:06.460 --> 00:36:08.530
JavaScript API does
this trick.

00:36:08.530 --> 00:36:08.905
AUDIENCE: OK.

00:36:08.905 --> 00:36:09.565
Well, thanks.

00:36:09.565 --> 00:36:12.350
AUDIENCE: But not if you're
using a styled map.

00:36:12.350 --> 00:36:14.968
SCOTT SHAWCROFT: But not if
